name: Verify login button in Buy and Sell CRO module

steps.name: When Navigate to CRO trade page
I click CROMarket by the xpath
I should see the ETHCROLink exist by the xpath
I use js click with CroUsdcLink by the css
Then Verify login button in Buy CRO module
I should see the LoginBtn_BuyCRO exist by the xpath
I click LoginBtn_BuyCRO by the xpath
I should see the Login_page_title exist by the xpath
I want the browser back to the last page
I should see the LoginBtn_SellCRO exist by the xpath
I click LoginBtn_SellCRO by the xpath
I should see the Login_page_title exist by the xpath

fullName: UI-Automation for CRO/USDC trade page: Verify login button in Buy and Sell CRO module
